data.title: Auburn School District
data.text:
Building for Learning

The Auburn School District Board of Directors has set a bond election for Tuesday, November 5. The bond will provide additional classrooms, improve safety and address critical systems.

ASD & APSF Host Welcome Back to School Event

All Auburn School District families are invited to the Welcome Back to School event from 3-6:00 p.m., August 15 at Auburn Memorial Stadium, 801 4th St NE.

SUN Meals Summer Food Program in ASD

Auburn School District continues to offer summer nutrition options to help our children reach their full potential. Read here for more information on the programs available.
